      "SelfBuffASiegfriedRegularBoss": {
        "id": "SelfBuffASiegfriedRegularBoss",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Cold Awakening",
          "description": "The user is granted a Charge, Sleep Ward, Poison Ward, Burn Shield and the Healing Burn status effect for 300TU. Then the user is Enraged, and will Endure the next damage that would defeat it with 1HP.\n\nUnlocked each time the user defeats a non-conjured enemy on the battlefield with an attack. This skill is locked again after each use.\n\nCertain skills are affected by and may consume charges. A unit can store a maximum of 3 charges, and all charges are removed from a unit that leaves the battlefield. Each Ward prevents their named effect from being applied once, then is removed. Identical Wards and Endure effects cannot stack. Burn Shields prevent the next non-burn status effect a unit would gain while Burning from applying. An Enraged unit's attack is increased to 1.5x until the end of their next turn. Enrage will overwrite any existing Weak or Enrage effects on the user.",
          "selected": "Burns, Endures, Enrages & Grants Wards\n(Will overwrite other status effects)"
        },
